Package socialmagnet.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This class is the entry point to start the Social Magnet application.
    CropController
    This Class represents the CropController class that contains the method to determine the yield of a crop
    FarmerController
    This Class represents the FarmerController class that contains the methods representing the actions that the farmer can perform
    MemberController
    This Class represents the MemberController that contains methods related to the Member class such as registering, login, showing a member's list of friends and friend requests, and creating a friend request.
    PostController
    This Class represents the PostController class that contains the methods related to the Post class.
    Session
    This Class represents the Session class.
    StoreController
    This Class represents the StoreController that contains methods related to the Store class.
